collection:
This can include information such as: your name, email address and username;
information about your device (e.g., IP address); and information relating to
how you use and interact with our sites, apps and services.

sharing:
INTERNATIONAL DATA TRANSFERS

To deliver services to you, it is sometimes necessary for us to transfer or
share your personal data outside the UK/EEA:

  * with our offices or other companies within our group located outside the UK/EEA;
  * with your and our service providers, e.g., cloud service providers, located outside the UK/EEA;
  * if you are based outside the UK/EEA;
  * where there is a European and/or international dimension to the services we are providing to you.
